children.text:
Thank you for choosing DaTuner to get you in-tune. This is the light, free and ad-free version of DaTuner. If you find DaTuner useful, want the latest and greatest version, or simply want to support its development, please consider using the "Pro" version.


==WHAT'S NEW IN 3.72==
 (3/4/2016)
-[Pro] Use list for temperaments selection, replacing the big knob.
-Bug fixes.

==WHAT'S NEW IN 3.71==
 (13/2/2016)
-Added a view of the noise floor level to assist in adjusting the trigger point manually (should have been in 3.70 but somehow got lost!)

==WHAT'S NEW IN 3.70==
 (10/2/2016)
-Switched Werckmeister I and III Temperaments in pro version.


==WHAT'S NEW IN 3.69==
 (27/1/2016)
-Screen and assets backgrounds set to BLACK
-Use graphics acceleration where available
-Handle screen rotation from settings activity to prevent losing the settings screen

==WHAT'S NEW IN 3.68==
 (27/7/2015)
-Small bug fix to default microphone source for recently updated versions.
